Package: TDWG
Title: Geographic Cleaning of Occurrence Records Using Taxonomic Databases for Plant Sciences
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Ian", "Ondo", email = "iondo@kew.org", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7816-5882"))
Description: This package contains multiple functions to select plant species and/or spatially filter occurrence records.
             It combines botanical information about ten of thousands of plant species from the Kew world checklist database with geographical information
             derived from The International Working Group on Taxonomic Databases for Plant Sciences (TDWG) at approximately "country" level and upwards.
License: What license it uses
